com.percussion.pso.transform
Class PSODateAdjust

java.lang.Object
  com.percussion.extension.PSDefaultExtension
      com.percussion.pso.transform.PSODateAdjust
All Implemented Interfaces:
com.percussion.extension.IPSExtension, com.percussion.extension.IPSFieldInputTransformer, com.percussion.extension.IPSUdfProcessor
public class PSODateAdjust
extends com.percussion.extension.PSDefaultExtension
implements com.percussion.extension.IPSFieldInputTransformer

A field input transform for setting one date field based on another. This works like the standard date adjust, except that it takes its source from a different field.

If the source date is blank (or not specified), then the current date and time are used.

Author:
davidbenua
